name: Experimentality Abstrakism of Verlin Santos #3
description:
While painting this, I'm listening to my latest poem entitled Ito na nga ba ang buhay?

𝐈𝐓𝐎 𝐍𝐀 𝐍𝐆𝐀 𝐁𝐀 𝐀𝐍𝐆 𝐁𝐔𝐇𝐀𝐘 talks about the life of an artist. There are always two sides of the situation. Both can be travelled by foot. It's up to you where to walk.

Digital: 4032x3022 pixels
Actual: 9x12 in
